#3시간 
def make_3_times_df(df):
    new_df = pd.DataFrame()
    for n in range(181):
        col_num = n * 18
        new_data = df.loc[col_num]
        new_df = pd.concat([new_df, new_data], axis=1)
    return new_df.T

#df plot

def df_plot(df1, df2, df3, df4, df5, df6, name1, name2, name3, name4, name5, name6):

    for i in col:
        plt.figure(figsize=(15, 10))
        plt.plot(df1[i], label=name1)
        plt.plot(df2[i], label=name2)
        plt.plot(df3[i], label=name3)
        plt.plot(df4[i], label=name4)
        plt.plot(df5[i], label=name5)
        plt.plot(df6[i], label=name6)

        plt.legend()
        plt.title(i)

        plt.show()

    return 1
